  <name>Cosmic Hot Corners</name>
  <summary>Hot corners daemon for the COSMIC™ desktop</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Cosmic Hot Corners is a background daemon that triggers configurable actions
      when the mouse pointer enters a screen corner. It supports multiple monitors
      and integrates natively with the COSMIC desktop ecosystem.
    </p>
    <p>Available actions per corner:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Show Workspaces overview</li>
      <li>Open App Launcher</li>
      <li>Run a custom shell command</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      Settings are configured through the included graphical interface.
      Changes apply instantly without restarting the daemon.
    </p>
  </description>
